      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/Conferences\" title=\"Conferences\">Conferences</a> * Advances in Computer Games 12</b>\n</p><p><b><a href=\"/Advances_in_Computer_Games_11\" title=\"Advances in Computer Games 11\">&lt; Prev</a> <a href=\"/Advances_in_Computer_Games_13\" title=\"Advances in Computer Games 13\">Next &gt;</a></b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:242px;\"><a href=\"http://www.cthnavarra.com/cth/web/cth/webcth.nsf/app/Obra/Palacio-Condestable\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/c/cf/MostrarImg.ashx.jpg\" width=\"240\" height=\"240\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:MostrarImg.ashx.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Palacio del Condestable <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div>\n<p>The <b>12th Advances in Computer Games</b> was held from May 11-13, <a href=\"/Timeline#2009\" title=\"Timeline\">2009</a>, at Palacio del Condestable, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pamplona\">Pamplona</a>,  <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Navarre\">Navarre</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Spain\">Spain</a>, in conjunction with the <a href=\"/WCCC_2009\" title=\"WCCC 2009\">17th World Computer Chess Championship</a> and the <a href=\"/14th_Computer_Olympiad\" title=\"14th Computer Olympiad\">14th Computer Olympiad</a>. ACG is the conference of the <a href=\"/ICGA\" title=\"ICGA\">ICGA</a>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Conference_Proceedings\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Conference Proceedings</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Lectures\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Lectures</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#See_also\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">See also</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Reports\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Reports</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Conference_Proceedings\">Conference Proceedings</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Advances_in_Computer_Games_12&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Conference Proceedings\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.springerlink.com/content/k723933hu624/?v=editorial\">Advances in Computer Games 12</a></li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a href=\"/Jaap_van_den_Herik\" title=\"Jaap van den Herik\">Jaap van den Herik</a>, <a href=\"/Pieter_Spronck\" title=\"Pieter Spronck\">Pieter Spronck</a> (eds.) (<b>2010</b>)</dd>\n<dd> Lecture Notes in Computer Science</dd>\n<dd> Springer Berlin / Heidelberg</dd>\n<dd> ISBN \t978-3-642-12992-6</dd></dl>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Lectures\">Lectures</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Advances_in_Computer_Games_12&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Lectures\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Matej_Guid\" title=\"Matej Guid\">Matej Guid</a>, <a href=\"/Martin_Mo%C5%BEina\" title=\"Martin Možina\">Martin Možina</a>, <a href=\"/Aleksander_Sadikov\" title=\"Aleksander Sadikov\">Aleksander Sadikov</a>, <a href=\"/Ivan_Bratko\" title=\"Ivan Bratko\">Ivan Bratko</a> (<b>2010</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.springerlink.com/content/um0l155681087p7h\">Deriving Concepts and Strategies from Chess Tablebases</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.ailab.si/matej/doc/Deriving_Concepts_and_Strategies_from_Chess_Tablebases.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=P%C3%A1lmi_Skowronski&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Pálmi Skowronski (page does not exist)\">Pálmi Skowronski</a>, <a href=\"/Yngvi_Bj%C3%B6rnsson\" title=\"Yngvi Björnsson\">Yngvi Björnsson</a>, <a href=\"/Mark_Winands\" title=\"Mark Winands\">Mark Winands</a> (<b>2010</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.sciweavers.org/publications/automated-discovery-search-extension-features\">Automated Discovery of Search-Extension Features</a></i>.  <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.hr.is/faculty/yngvi/pdf/SkowronskiBW09.pdf\">pdf</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/Search\" title=\"Search\">Search</a>, <a href=\"/Extensions\" title=\"Extensions\">Extensions</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Markus_Enzenberger\" title=\"Markus Enzenberger\">Markus Enzenberger</a>, <a href=\"/Martin_M%C3%BCller\" title=\"Martin Müller\">Martin Müller</a> (<b>2010</b>). <i>A lock-free multithreaded Monte-Carlo tree search algorithm</i>.  <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://webdocs.cs.ualberta.ca/~mmueller/ps/enzenberger-mueller-acg12.pdf\">pdf</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/Monte-Carlo_Tree_Search\" title=\"Monte-Carlo Tree Search\">Monte-Carlo Tree Search</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Guillaume_Chaslot\" title=\"Guillaume Chaslot\">Guillaume Chaslot</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Christophe_Fiter&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Christophe Fiter (page does not exist)\">Christophe Fiter</a>, <a href=\"/Jean-Baptiste_Hoock\" title=\"Jean-Baptiste Hoock\">Jean-Baptiste Hoock</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Arpad_Rimmel&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Arpad Rimmel (page does not exist)\">Arpad Rimmel</a>, <a href=\"/Olivier_Teytaud\" title=\"Olivier Teytaud\">Olivier Teytaud</a> (<b>2010</b>). <i>Adding Expert Knowledge and Exploration in Monte-Carlo Tree Search</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.personeel.unimaas.nl/g-chaslot/papers/acg09.pdf\">pdf</a>&#160;» </li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Fabien_Teytaud\" title=\"Fabien Teytaud\">Fabien Teytaud</a>, <a href=\"/Olivier_Teytaud\" title=\"Olivier Teytaud\">Olivier Teytaud</a> (<b>2010</b>). <i>Creating an Upper-Confidence-Tree program for Havannah</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://hal.inria.fr/docs/00/38/05/39/PDF/hav.pdf\">pdf</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/UCT\" title=\"UCT\">UCT</a>, <a href=\"/Havannah\" title=\"Havannah\">Havannah</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Tristan_Cazenave\" title=\"Tristan Cazenave\">Tristan Cazenave</a> (<b>2010</b>). <i>Monte-Carlo Kakuro</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.lamsade.dauphine.fr/~cazenave/papers/kakuro.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Philip_Henderson&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Philip Henderson (page does not exist)\">Philip Henderson</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Broderick_Arneson&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Broderick Arneson (page does not exist)\">Broderick Arneson</a>, <a href=\"/Ryan_Hayward\" title=\"Ryan Hayward\">Ryan Hayward</a> (<b>2010</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.springerlink.com/content/y8298h5713143289/\">Hex, Braids, the Crossing Rule, and XH-Search</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://webdocs.cs.ualberta.ca/~hayward/papers/xhsearch.pdf\">pdf</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/Hex\" title=\"Hex\">Hex</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Gerhard_Trippen&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Gerhard Trippen (page does not exist)\">Gerhard Trippen</a> (<b>2010</b>). <i>Plans, Patterns and Move Categories Guiding a Highly Selective Search</i>.  <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://arimaa.com/arimaa/papers/0905Trippen/Contribution118.pdf\">pdf</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/Arimaa\" title=\"Arimaa\">Arimaa</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Jahn-Takeshi_Saito\" title=\"Jahn-Takeshi Saito\">Jahn-Takeshi Saito</a>, <a href=\"/Mark_Winands\" title=\"Mark Winands\">Mark Winands</a>, <a href=\"/Jaap_van_den_Herik\" title=\"Jaap van den Herik\">Jaap van den Herik</a> (<b>2010</b>). <i>Randomized Parallel Proof-Number Search</i>.  <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://wwwis.win.tue.nl/bnaic2009/papers/bnaic2009_paper_23.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Eiko_Bleicher\" title=\"Eiko Bleicher\">Eiko Bleicher</a>, <a href=\"/Guy_Haworth\" title=\"Guy Haworth\">Guy McCrossan Haworth</a> (<b>2010</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://centaur.reading.ac.uk/4518/\">6-Man Chess and Zugzwangs</a></i>. </li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Joe_Leslie-Hurd\" title=\"Joe Leslie-Hurd\">Joe Hurd</a>, <a href=\"/Guy_Haworth\" title=\"Guy Haworth\">Guy McCrossan Haworth</a> (<b>2010</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007%2F978-3-642-12993-3_20\">Data Assurance in Opaque Computations</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.gilith.com/research/papers/egt.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Guy_Haworth\" title=\"Guy Haworth\">Guy McCrossan Haworth</a>, <a href=\"/Kenneth_W._Regan\" title=\"Kenneth W. Regan\">Ken Regan</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Giuseppe_Di_Fatta&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Giuseppe Di Fatta (page does not exist)\">Giuseppe Di Fatta</a> (<b>2010</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007%2F978-3-642-12993-3_10\">Performance and Prediction: Bayesian Modelling of Fallible Choice in Chess</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.cse.buffalo.edu/faculty/regan/papers/pdf/HRdF10.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Bo-Nian_Chen\" title=\"Bo-Nian Chen\">Bo-Nian Chen</a>, <a href=\"/Pangfeng_Liu\" title=\"Pangfeng Liu\">Pangfeng Liu</a>, <a href=\"/Shun-Chin_Hsu\" title=\"Shun-Chin Hsu\">Shun-Chin Hsu</a>, <a href=\"/Tsan-sheng_Hsu\" title=\"Tsan-sheng Hsu\">Tsan-sheng Hsu</a> (<b>2010</b>). <i>Conflict Resolution of Chinese Chess Endgame Knowledge Base</i>.</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Li-Te_Huang\" title=\"Li-Te Huang\">Li-Te Huang</a>, <a href=\"/Shun-Shii_Lin\" title=\"Shun-Shii Lin\">Shun-Shii Lin</a> (<b>2010</b>). <i>Optimal Analyses for 3×n AB Games in the Worst Case</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.rosenbaum-games.de/3m/p1/Mastermind/2009LiTe01.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Istv%C3%A1n_Szita\" title=\"István Szita\">István Szita</a>, <a href=\"/Guillaume_Chaslot\" title=\"Guillaume Chaslot\">Guillaume Chaslot</a>, <a href=\"/Pieter_Spronck\" title=\"Pieter Spronck\">Pieter Spronck</a> (<b>2010</b>). <i>Monte-Carlo Tree Search in Settlers of Catan</i>.  <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://ticc.uvt.nl/~pspronck/pubs/ACG12Szita.pdf\">pdf</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Advances_in_Computer_Games_12&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: See also\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/14th_Computer_Olympiad\" title=\"14th Computer Olympiad\">14th Computer Olympiad</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/WCCC_2009\" title=\"WCCC 2009\">WCCC 2009</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Reports\">Reports</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Advances_in_Computer_Games_12&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Reports\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Richard_J._Lorentz\" title=\"Richard J. Lorentz\">Richard J. Lorentz</a> (<b>2009</b>). <i>The Advances in Computer Games Conference 2009.</i>  <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#32_2\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 32, No. 2</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Dap_Hartmann\" title=\"Dap Hartmann\">Dap Hartmann</a> (<b>2010</b>). <i>Human Superiority Restored</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#33_3\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 33, No. 3</a>, Review revised papers, edited by <a href=\"/Jaap_van_den_Herik\" title=\"Jaap van den Herik\">Jaap van den Herik</a> and <a href=\"/Pieter_Spronck\" title=\"Pieter Spronck\">Pieter Spronck</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Advances_in_Computer_Games_12&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://ilk.uvt.nl/icga/acg12/index.html\">Advances in Computer Games 12</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://get.google.com/albumarchive/117053534374902710729/album/AF1QipM5Wr00KdHRue7XOO67QRA3-B2ClTHDqlzlAjMj\">Album archive - 14th Computer Olympiad Pamplona</a> by <a href=\"/Hideki_Kato\" title=\"Hideki Kato\">Hideki Kato</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsectio